Pour 700ml/1Â¼ pint freshly boiled water into a saucepan, add the stock cube and stir well to dissolve. Add the noodles, spring onions, peas and chicken, bring to the boil and cook for 5 minutes, or until the noodles and peas are cooked and the chicken is hot through.Ladle into a deep, wide bowl and, if you fancy, top with the chilli, ginger, garlic, coriander and soy.